						               													<description>Land of legends is a board game that will intrigue any and all fans of strategic and PvP type battles. The number of player may vary from 2 to 4 with an age limit of 13 and up. The rules of the game are very simple.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The main objective of the game is to rule over the entire island.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the Land of Legends game there are 2 races: human and undead.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At first you have to choose between those races, as well as the place where player want to place his castle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Locations of castles can be established through discussion, if positions cannot be agreed upon players must roll the dice to establish castle placement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game there are two playing fields: The World Map and The City. The World Map is where you will send your armies to battle your opponents and capture enemy castles; throwing dice will move your army in the direction of your choosing. During your journeys you will encounter bonuses and obstacles. Also during your journey throughout the world map you can develop your castle. While on the playing field of the World Map players will land on certain places that will move them to the City Map where they will have the opportunity to hire mercenaries such as: Wizards, Archers, Swordsmen and Horsemen. Players will also be able to buy or find various artifacts and potions for their hero.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
